title: Haunted Temple of Birinn
story: For centuries the temple of Birinn remained uninhabited. Lately a pack of spectral pigeons have made its home here.

notes.text: A great door with a keyhole on the northern wall.
A weird, covered with glyphs lamp hovering in the middle of the large room.
A corpse of a dwarf, a lily-shaped key close to it.
A painting on the wall depicting the land around the temple.
Arrows and some gold among rubble on the ground.
